{"tid":1610842,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"今日你哋可以返工返學","createTime":"2019-10-01T21:39:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-01T21:53:55.000Z","uid":308530,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"6a4501dd0f63edcafeb8cdb088151d52402cbb42","tid":1610842,"uid":308530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T21:39:05.000Z","msg":"但係請將跳閘變成最低消費好唔好<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DgAPRex.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDgAPRex.jpg&h=79f32e34&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n望撚住呢張相 知唔知道琴日幾多人返唔到屋企 <br />\n我哋要畀呢條仆街賣幾多次先滿意<br />\n我明白有啲工種可能唔射得波 返學嘅都要顧住自己DSE GPA<br />\n但請你哋唔好忘記將抗爭融入自己生活 咁樣先係長而有效的方法<br />\n所以大家應承香港人 要喺每一種生活小細節入面開始做出改變 <br />\n好唔好<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfbef024f32dc16587a71b59a37072647a6c6063","tid":1610842,"uid":51598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T21:53:55.000Z","msg":"推"}]}